Release history for Data-Downloader

Version 0.9907 2012-11-24
  - dependency fix

Version 0.9906 2012-11-19
  - various bug fixes
  - improved docs and added references to datacasting and esip

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version 0.9905 2012-10-11
 - removed system find from tests

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version 0.9904 2012-10-09
 - required DADO_TESTS for dado cli tests

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version 0.9903  2012-10-05
 - merged version 0.52
 - various test and doc fixes

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version 0.9902  2012-10-04
 - fixed up dependencies

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version 0.9901  2012-10-03
 - initial public release

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version 0.52

 - Use immediate transaction for file->remove to force exclusive lock
 - Added "list" method for files; enabled "dado files list" action
 - Changed default database for testing; Removed environment variable
   DATA_DOWNLOADER_TMPDIR and added DATA_DOWNLOADER_TESTDB

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version 0.51  2012-07-31

 - RDF items without filenames are now skipped
 - Created module for unit test functions
 - Made unit tests modular and self-cleaning
 - Added ERRORDIE and LOGDIE functions
 - Changed log level for non-fatal errors
 - Enabled immediate transactions for live database
 - Moved to standardize environment variables

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version 0.50  2012-07-30

 - Updated dado_remove_links (Phil)

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version 0.49  2012-06-29

 - Added dado_remove_links (Phil)

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version 0.48  2012-06-06

 - Recover from failed purge
 - Better handling of download directory
 - Don't LOGDIE on all errors

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version 0.47  2012-04-16

 - dadod fix for new mojo
 - load_from_urn when a matching file is found

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version 0.46  2011-10-26

 - Follow redirects

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version 0.45  2012-04-16

 - Fix for dbd::sqlite 1.31

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version 0.44  2011-07-22

 - Added dadod
 - More race condition handling
 - Made "use" idempotent
 - Require newer SQLite (for immediate transactions)
 - Fixed transaction logic
 - Added DADO_MAX_TIME_PER_FILE

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Version 0.43  2011-03-22

 - Fixed logic for checking existing links in decorate_tree()
 - Fixed 02-mds.t to respect DATA_DOWNLOADER_BULK_DOWNLOAD variable
 - Updated tests for OMI SIPS port (8201 -> 8000)
 - Fixed logic in _choose_disk (update $self->disk_obj)

------------------------------------------------------------------------

